	* Vic Cherubini <vmc@leftnode.com> Because PDO allocates memory for each field, allocating a ton of memory for the form data only to not use it is unecessary. Thus, I updated this to only select the data and errors fields since they're the only ones used. I also made the fields regular text fields rather than longtext to help with the memory allocation. (06:42:01)

